  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264420/extras/a9f532ef208411583a933a07bf34bc6d.avif?t=1678707577\" width=650 height=178 /></span><br><br><strong>Take your bow and start the adventure to reveal the big secret!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264420/extras/d4a3d168d389b3e167de996d6472554e.avif?t=1678707577\" width=500 height=262 /></span><br><br><strong>A fun adventure is waiting for you ! Different maps, places, characters and bows.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264420/extras/84a44ea69b7442529ebd1daee6af3305.avif?t=1678707577\" width=500 height=262 /></span><br><br><strong>After complete all the levels, a secret level will be open. You will learn the big secret !</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264420/extras/351e80f8ebef1fdfea2fb4261fb4b7be.avif?t=1678707577\" width=500 height=262 /></span><br><br><strong>This is not just simulator game! There is a mini story in the game. After complete the normal levels, the secret section and the surprise ending are opened!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264420/extras/2788da43cc6cd0a96d85e631e75107ac.avif?t=1678707577\" width=500 height=262 /></span>",
